entry.title: ceciliamay/obsidianmd-theme-primary
entry.summary: Primary is a warm, playful but productive theme for Obsidian. Its colors were inspired by Bauhaus, Scandinavian interior, and yellowing retro magazine pages. It has been described as chill and having vibes of "freshly baked goods".
